StructureDefinition-CareConnect-PractitionerRole-1

The PractitionerRole resource represents a specific set of Roles/Locations/specialties/services that a practitioner may perform at an organization for a period of time.

Profile Minimum Viable Content (MVC)

This FHIR profile has no mandatory elements.

Formal Views of Profile Content

Description of Profiles, Differentials, and Snapshots.

The official URL for this profile is: https://fhir.hl7.org.uk/STU3/StructureDefinition/CareConnect-PractitionerRole-1

Published on Mon Nov 05 00:00:00 GMT 2018 as draft by HL7 UK.
